text: Anton Mikhailavich Prylepau is an archer from Belarus. Prylepau competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics and the 2016 Summer Olympics. He was born on 5 February 1984.Anton Prylepau == References == Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian archers Category:Olympians for Belarus
